parameters:
???: You, Zerachiel. I have been
waiting for you to come.

????: Don't worry. I'm just stopping
time to have a conversation with you.

Zerachiel: Control the flow of time in
the world...? That shouldn't be
possible...

Zerachiel: Ah, you're the one I spoke to
on the ship!!

????: That's right. Let's greet each
other first.

????: I am Orpheus, the foolish god who
created the Seventh Curse.

Orpheus: That's right. I have been
watching over you all this time.

Orpheus: That lewd mark is the cause of
everything.

Orpheus: The lewd mark is something I
created.

Orpheus: I have been watching over
everything through the element of the
lewd mark.

Orpheus: You are a homunculus, yet you
possess self-awareness and strive to
help the saint.

Orpheus: Your actions are quite
interesting.

Orpheus: You went to a dangerous place
to help the saint.

Orpheus: I fought against goblins in the
scorching desert.

Orpheus: I drove away the Lamia in the
Magic Ore Mountain.

Orpheus: I defeated the giant of flames
in the underground volcano and was
attacked by monster girls in the Starry
Forest.

Orpheus: You went that far to protect
the saint...

Orpheus: ...You tried to save the
descendant of my clan.

Orpheus: I express my heartfelt
gratitude.

Zerachiel: As I thought, that dream was
real.

Zerachiel: So, Effy is of Orpheus'
bloodline.

Orpheus: The saint Effy is my... the
evil god Orpheus' last descendant.

Zerachiel: Last... What about the rest
of your family?

Orpheus: When Effy was born, her parents
died in a tragic accident.

Orpheus: The parents mentioned in that
diary were just adoptive parents. Effy
is all alone in this world.
Zerachiel: So that's how it was...

Zerachiel: So, did you protect Effy in
the cult?

Orpheus: No, I have been watching over
Effy, but I haven't interfered.

Orpheus: Bringing her to the cult was
the work of someone else.

Zerachiel: Another person... could it
be...

Orpheus: Yes, the cult leader... the
star god Eden.

Orpheus: The star god Eden knows the
terror of the Seventh Curse.

Orpheus: I suppose they thought that by
obtaining that power, they would be able
to dominate the world...

Orpheus: I searched desperately and
found Effy.

Orpheus: In order to steal the power of
the Seventh Curse.

Zerachiel: ...Is that why you became the
leader of the Orpheus Cult?

Zerachiel: What was the reason for
putting a curse on Effy?

Orpheus: It was to obtain the power of
the Seventh Curse.

Orpheus: When I sealed the Seventh
Curse, I set up multiple barriers.

Orpheus: Even though it's a star god,
it's not something that can be easily
broken.

Orpheus: However, the strength of the
barrier depends on the element of the
holder.

Orpheus: Due to the power of the Seventh
Curse, Effy possessed a high level of
elemental energy...

Orpheus: If we can weaken that element,
it will be easier to break through the
barrier.

Orpheus: The star god set its sights
there.

Zerachiel: Did you curse Effy for that
reason...

Orpheus: The star god is that kind of
person.

Orpheus: Anticipating this outcome, I
was thinking of somehow saving Effy.

Orpheus: In order to save Effy, who was
cursed and became a sacrifice by the
star god, I was thinking...
Orpheus: I can entrust this to you.
Zerachiel: Entrust? What do you mean...?
Orpheus: ...A way to stop the star god.

Orpheus: The power of the Seventh Curse
has already been absorbed by the star
god.

Orpheus: Now that it has come to this,
in order to stop the Seventh Curse, we
need to defeat the star god.

Orpheus: That's why I want to entrust it
to you.

Orpheus: The power to defeat the star
god...

Orpheus: In the war a thousand years
ago, I unleashed the Seventh Curse and
took many lives.

Orpheus: I feel responsible. That's why
I want to stop the Seventh Curse.

Orpheus: And I want to free the
descendant of our clan... Effy... from
the curse...

Zerachiel: About unleashing the Seventh
Curse...

Zerachiel: The fact that we couldn't
defeat the star god...

Orpheus: What I have done is
unforgivable. It is only natural that I
bear the stigma of the evil god.
Zerachiel: No, you are not an evil god.

Zerachiel: The divine being who tried to
save the world.

Zerachiel: Orpheus tried to save the
world, right?

Zerachiel: As a result, many lives were
lost.

Zerachiel: But you see, it's not like I
made the wrong choice.

Zerachiel: You ended the quagmire of
war.

Zerachiel: You're a splendid divine
being.

Orpheus: ...The only one who called me
the Divine Being was you.

Zerachiel: I recognize you as a divine
being.

Zerachiel: So, please. I want you to
lend me your power.
Zerachiel: I want to save Effy.

Orpheus: I shall entrust everything to
you... The Eighth Curse!
CL: I'm counting on you, Zerachiel...

Zerachiel has acquired \c[6]Orpheus'
Blessing\c[0]. All stats will increase.

By using it during battle, your attack
power, magic power, and defense power
will be \c[6]doubled\c[0].

Zerachiel has learned the \c[6]Promise
of the White Wings\c[0].
Rabi: Your eyes have turned red.
Lala: No, this is more like red...
Zerachiel: It's true, I... I'm crying...

Zerachiel: (The power entrusted to me by
you... I will definitely not waste it)

Zerachiel: (I'll do my best. I'll defeat
the Star God. So...)

Zerachiel: (...Please continue to watch
over me.)
